## 🚀 Quick Start

This is a pnpm-based monorepo powered by Turbo for optimal build performance and developer experience.

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18.0.0 or higher
- pnpm 8.0.0 or higher

### Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Setup git hooks
pnpm prepare
```

### Development

```bash
# Start all apps in development mode
pnpm dev

# Start specific app
pnpm --filter <app-name> dev
```

### Building

```bash
# Build all packages and apps
pnpm build

# Build specific package
pnpm --filter <package-name> build
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
pnpm test

# Run unit tests only
pnpm test:unit

# Run integration tests
pnpm test:integration

# Run E2E tests
pnpm test:e2e

# Generate coverage reports
pnpm test:coverage
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Lint all packages
pnpm lint

# Fix linting issues
pnpm lint:fix

# Type checking
pnpm typecheck

# Format code
pnpm format

# Check formatting
pnpm format:check
```

## 📁 Project Structure

```
{{ monorepo_name }}/
├── apps/                    # Applications (Next.js, Express, etc.)
│   └── web/                # Web applications
├── packages/               # Shared packages and utilities
│   ├── ui/                # UI components
│   ├── config/            # Shared configuration
│   └── utils/             # Utility functions
├── docs/                   # Documentation
├── .github/                # GitHub workflows
├── turbo.json             # Turbo configuration
